### Smart Classroom API - Recognition Endpoints
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### Variables are loaded from .env file

@baseUrl = http://{{$dotenv API_HOST}}:{{$dotenv API_PORT}}
@apiKey = {{$dotenv API_KEY}}

### ===========================================
### Single Recognition Endpoints
### ===========================================

### Save face recognition
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/save
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "person_name": "John Doe",
    "camera_id": "camera_01",
    "confidence_score": 0.95
}

###

### Get all recognition logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/logs?skip=0&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Get specific recognition log by ID
# Replace {log_id} with actual ID from database
@logId = YOUR_LOG_ID_HERE
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/logs/{{logId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Filter recognition logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/filter?person_name=John&camera_id=camera_01&skip=0&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Filter by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/filter?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-12-31&skip=0&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Update recognition log
# Replace logId above with actual log ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/logs/{{logId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "person_name": "Updated Name",
    "confidence_score": 0.98
}

###

### Delete recognition log
# Replace logId above with actual log ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/logs/{{logId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### ===========================================
### Batch Recognition Endpoints
### ===========================================

### Process image for batch face recognition
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batch/process
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "image_path": "/media/magesh/NewVolume4/Images/Training/ICC 2011/Team.webp"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batch/process
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "image_path": "/media/magesh/NewVolume4/Images/Training/ICC 2011/squad.jpg"
}

###

### Get batch results by batch ID
# Replace with actual batch ID from process response
@batchId = YOUR_BATCH_ID_HERE
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batch/{{batchId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Get all batch summaries
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batches?skip=0&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### ⚠️ DELETE all batch recognition logs (DANGEROUS!)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batches
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}



### ===========================================
### Add Persons Endpoints
### ===========================================

### Add persons from default folder (datasets/new_persons/)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/persons/add
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "source_path": null,
    "move_to_backup": true
}


### Add persons from specific folder (folder path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/persons/add
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "source_path": "/media/magesh/NewVolume4/Images/Training/ICC 2011/Players",
    "move_to_backup": true
}

###




POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batch/process
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "image_path": "/media/magesh/NewVolume4/Images/Training/ICC 2011/squad.jpg"
}



### Get all known persons in database
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/persons
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ⚠️ DELETE all batch recognition logs (DANGEROUS!)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batches
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}